ziness: This may occur due to a drop in blood pressure or imbalance, and can happen when standing up quickly or during sudden movements.", "Flushing: Often experienced as a side effect due to the dilation of blood vessels, resulting in a temporary reddening of the face.", "Palpitations: Patients may experience a sensation of the heart beating faster or irregularly, which can occur due to changes in heart rhythm."]}}